                                <br>
                                - Charges
                                <span style="color:#89AF07; font-size:15px; font-weight:700; line-height: 19px;">0.00 FCFA</span>

                                <br>
                                - TVA
                                <span style="color:#89AF07; font-size:15px; font-weight:700; line-height: 19px;">0.00 FCFA</span>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>


        </div>
    </div>



